statements.sql: select `conduits`.`id`, `title`, `about`, `detail`, `tag`, `conduits`.`created_at`, `users`.`name` from `conduits` inner join `users` on `users`.`id` = `conduits`.`user_id` where `conduits`.`id` = '1' limit 1

select `post_forms`.`id`, `comment`, `post_forms`.`created_at`, `users`.`name`, `article_id` from `post_forms` inner join `users` on `users`.`id` = `post_forms`.`user_id` inner join `conduits` on `conduits`.`id` = `post_forms`.`article_id` where `article_id` = '1'
